      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, i'm working on a paper about AI cognitive limits and i really want to aim for nature with this one. i have a rough draft of the abstract but it feels a bit weak. can you help me polish it so it sounds more authoritative and high-impact? here is what i have so far:\n\n\"This study looks at how AI models process complex logic. We tested several models and found that they struggle with certain cognitive biases. Our findings suggest that current LLMs have specific limits in reasoning.\"",
