      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, 50 models and 20 benchmarks? i don't think we actually ran that many tests. i only did a small pilot with about 10 participants for the first phase to see if the logic held up. are you sure we should be claiming such a huge scale in the abstract? wouldn't that be risky if they ask for the raw data?",
